# HFT: aggregate book depth by summing top-N quantities.
*depth(qs as Vec of i64, n as i64) returns i64
    s is 0
    i is 0
    while i < n
        s is s + qs.get(i)
        i is i + 1
    s

*main
    qs is vec()
    qs.push(10)
    qs.push(20)
    qs.push(15)
    qs.push(5)
    qs.push(100)
    log depth(qs, 3)
